# CoRails
Canonical register for CoCivium rails (BPOE, CoVows, CoProtocats, protocol rules).

**Rule:** chat is not the ledger. All rails live here (or in vault) as versioned files + receipts.

## Structure
- ledger/CoRails_Ledger.ndjson (append-only events)
- ules/*.md (canonical rules)
- generated/ (register outputs)
- eceipts/ (sha receipts)
- scripts/ (rebuild/validate tooling)

## One command
Run:
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\scripts\CoRails_Rebuild.ps1 -CoRailsRoot .
"@ | Set-Content -LiteralPath README.md -Encoding utf8

@"
*.sha256 text eol=lf
*.md    text eol=lf
*.ps1   text eol=lf
